1	0.000000000	6a:df:73:aa:ed:3b	Broadcast	ARP	42	Who has 10.0.0.3? Tell 10.0.0.1\
2	0.019249269	4a:3f:17:2f:0e:b3	6a:df:73:aa:ed:3b	ARP	42	10.0.0.3 is at 4a:3f:17:2f:0e:b3\
